The first time I actually got curious about cryptocurrency, is when I became more active on Twitter seeing many post about cryptoart.

I invested 50$ in Tezos without having a clue what it was or how it worked. Just that it was more than enough for minting on hicetnunc.

First off, what is a Ledger? For someone that is not a native english speaker, as myself, this word can sound a bit foreign. A 'ledger' is what's at the very core of a cryptocurrency.
